  "embodiment": "Multi-Chip Stand Alone",
  "description": "The GlobalProtect App is a software cryptographic module that runs on commercially available operating systems and mobile devices to provide security for users. The GlobalProtect App secures traffic using TLS or IPsec, and allows users to connect to corporate networks to access their company's resources from anywhere in the world.",
